Swtich Expression:
single variable having multiple choice is where swtich is used normal swtuch doesn't return value whereas swtich expression do return value
yield work as return in swtich expression

shield class and record class
consumer interface have a method name accept 

Stream API - a sequence of elements that can be proceed in a pipeline of opreations such as filtering,mapping,sorting and reducing.
one opreation output will be the input for other opreation
streams dont store data anywhere it only perform opreations and then you need to store it into a list manually
collection to stream - Collection.stream() 
array to stream - Arrays.stream()
direct stream - Stream.of()
Stream.iterate(strating,condition) and Stream.genrate() // not in syllabus
All stream API are divided into 2 parts:-
Intermediate opreation- filter, map, distinct, sort,limit() etc.( only give the form not the result give result with terminal operation)
Terminal Opreation - forEach,reduce,collect,count etc. (give result)

